{{Infobox musical artist | honorific_prefix = | name = Costantino Carrara | honorific_suffix = | image = | image_upright = | image_size = | landscape = | alt = | caption = | background = non_vocal_instrumentalist | native_name = | native_name_lang = | birth_name = | alias = | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1997|04|18}} | birth_place = [[Bitonto]], [[Bari]], [[Italy]] | origin = [[Italy]] | death_date = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} (death date first) --> | death_place = | genre = [[Pop music|Pop]], [[Instrumental]], [[Classical crossover]] | occupation = [[Pianist]], [[composer]] | instrument = [[Piano]] | years_active = 2011–present | label = | associated_acts = | website = {{URL|http://costantinocarrara.com/}} | module = {{Infobox YouTube personality|embed=yes |pseudonym = |years active = 2011–present |genre = Music |channel_name= kosta97piano |catchphrase(s) = |subscribers = 600+ thousand |views = 100+ million |view_date = |subscriber_date = |network = |associated_acts = |silver_button = yes |silver_year = 2016 |gold_button = |gold_year = |diamond_button = |diamond_year = |stats_update = September 25, 2018 }} | module2 = | module3 = }}
'''Costantino Carrara''' (born April 18, 1997 in [[Bitonto]]) is an Italian pianist and composer known for his popular piano arrangements uploaded on YouTube.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://video.repubblica.it/spettacoli-e-cultura/costantino-da-nerd-a-youtube-star-un-sogno-realizzato-al-pianoforte/304737/305368|title=Costantino, da "nerd" a YouTube star: un sogno realizzato al pianoforte|newspaper=Repubblica|date=14 May 2018|accessdate=10 October 2018|language=it}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lastampa.it/2016/06/22/tecnologia/marcello-e-costantino-la-maturit-degli-youtuber-coSStqGcbBaGnlonEfUgHP/pagina.html|title=Marcello e Costantino, la maturità degli youtuber|work=La Stampa|date=21 June 2016|accessdate=10 October 2018|language=it}}</ref> His most viewed video of all time is his arrangement of "Let Her Go" by [[Passenger]].
== Career == In 2016 Carrara set up a crowdfunding campaign for his WildPianos project, which proposes to bring piano music in nature. In the same year, the music brand [[Yamaha]] joined the project. Carrara shoot the first video in the series in the Apulian inland.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Caldara |first1=Marta |title=Costantino Carrara, un canale su YouTube per far conoscere il suo talento |url=https://www.yamahamusicclub.it/sali-sul-palco/costantino-carrara-un-canale-su-youtube-per-far-conoscere-il-suo-talento/ |website=Yamaha Music Club |publisher=Yamaha Corporation |language=Italian|trans-title=Constantine Carrara, a YouTube channel to let his talents know|accessdate=10 October 2018 |date=15 March 2017}}</ref>
