'''Jadon and Anias McDonald''' are a pair of formerly conjoined [[craniopagus]] [[Twin|twins]]. They were separated in a nearly 30 hour [[surgery]] on October 14, 2016<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.today.com/health/formerly-conjoined-twins-are-home-enjoying-life-toddlers-t117926|title=Formerly conjoined twins are finally home 1 year after epic surgery|work=TODAY.com|access-date=2018-11-18|language=en-US}}</ref> at Children's Hospital at [[Montefiore Medical Center|Montefiore]] when they were thirteen months old.<ref name="today">{{cite news |last1=Holohan |first1=Meghan |title=Formerly conjoined twins are finally home 1 year after epic surgery |url=https://www.today.com/health/formerly-conjoined-twins-are-home-enjoying-life-toddlers-t117926 |accessdate=27 June 2018 |publisher=Today |date=2017-10-26}}</ref><ref name="cnnhome">{{cite news |last1=Drash |first1=Wayne |title=The formerly conjoined McDonald twins' amazing journey home |url=https://www.cnn.com/2017/09/07/health/conjoined-twins-go-home-main/index.html |accessdate=27 June 2018 |work=CNN |date=2017-09-07}}</ref>
Less than a year after they were separated, they returned home to their house in New York's Orange County to live with parents, Nicole and Chrisitian, and older brother, Aza.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2017/09/07/health/conjoined-twins-go-home-main/index.html|title=Bringing home formerly conjoined twins|last=CNN|first=Story by Wayne Drash, CNN Video by Roni Selig, Al DiSanti and Priscilla Thompson,|work=CNN|access-date=2018-11-18}}</ref> Before they were separated, the boys and family lived in the [[The Bronx|Bronx]] but they purchased the home in foreclosure while the boys were in rehab at [[Blythedale Children's Hospital]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2017/09/07/health/conjoined-twins-go-home-main/index.html|title=Bringing home formerly conjoined twins|last=CNN|first=Story by Wayne Drash, CNN Video by Roni Selig, Al DiSanti and Priscilla Thompson,|work=CNN|access-date=2018-11-18}}</ref> At home, they will have 20 hours a week of in-home therapy. <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.today.com/health/formerly-conjoined-twins-are-home-enjoying-life-toddlers-t117926|title=Formerly conjoined twins are finally home 1 year after epic surgery|work=TODAY.com|access-date=2018-11-18|language=en-US}}</ref>
